# Why 'open science'?


## Rapid progress

- Copy, attribute, modify, share

## Reproducibility 
- TEst [1](http://cnn.com)

## Economic

- Science funding
- Internationally
- School systems

## Social

- Democratization
- 'Small Data'

# Is it realistic?

## Yes.

- Server software
- NASA
- Biology
- ArXiv
- Wikipedia
- Sparkfun and Adafruit

## But:

- Tenure
- Commercial interests & patents
- Cultural norms
- Legacy
- Rigidity of high school curricula

