# Arduino

<img src="http://arduino.cc/en/uploads/Main/arduino_due_in_hand.jpg" height=200>

## Single Processor

- 32 kB memory
- 16 MHz clock

## One program

- setup()
- loop()
- No operating system

## Input and output 'pins'

- measure voltages
- apply voltages
- input, output, control
- 'physical computing'

## Tutorials

